sp.p:
 Aye, and the people were as wretched in it;
what a mist of Tobacco 

flew amongst them?

Well Signior Lionell, you are beholding to these Gentlemen,
for their good words unto your Uncles for you, they spoke in your behalf,
as earnestly, as ever did Lawyer for his Client.

 A piece of Antiquity, Sir; it is English coin;
and if you will 

needs know, it is an old Harry groat.

 Some queasy stomach might turn, perhaps, at such a motion; 

but I am more resolved, better hardened:  what is he?  for I have my 

several rates, salaries for blood; for a Lord, so much;
for a Knight, 

so much; a Gentleman, so much; a Peasant, so much; a
Stranger, so 

much; and a Native, so much.

 Not till you are better tempered:  what I have revealed, is true; 

and though you prove unthankful, good deeds reward themselves, the 

conscience of the fact shall pay my virtue; so I leave you.

 Master  Aurelio,  good morrow to you;
whose chamber is that 

I pray?

 Thank you Gentlemen, and I to either of you no worse fortune; 

but that my wife is not yet risen, I would entreat you take the 

pains come up and visit her.

To marry me, for the safeguard of your credit, and that suddenly;
for I have made a vow, that unless you will do it without delay,
I will not have you at all.

An old Lesson? yes, he shall play the beginning of the world;
and for a song, he shall sing one that was made to the moving of the
Orbs, when they were first set in tune.

None alas against you, you are virtuous, but you think you
can act the Iupiter, to blind me with your escapes, and concealed trulls;
yet I am not so simple, but I can play the Iuno, and find out your exploits.

 Why, the supposed boy you seem to be jealous of, it is your 

own Lemon, you own deer morsel; I have searched out the mystery; 

husbands must do ill, and wives must bear the reproach; a fine inversion.
